name: Polymer Clay Octopus Tentacle Earrings (Purple, Lilac, White, Black)
description:
These earrings are made out of lightweight polymer clay in purple, lilac, black and white.

In some cases these pictures are representative and not of the actual item. I can make these nearly identical to each other but since it is handmade slight variations between each one will occur. Yours may slightly differ in color/shape. They are all coated in a layer of varnish for extra sliminess. 


*******Alterations**********
-I can make these into any colors you want.
-These can also be made into a pendant.
